node.text:
While hubby cooks lunch and dinner , I made desserts ! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Ta-Dah , check out my bowl of 𝐈𝐜𝐲 𝐘𝐚𝐤𝐮𝐥𝐭 𝐋𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐚𝐧𝐬 𝐏𝐮𝐧𝐜𝐡 ! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Simply mix some crushed ice , jellies , longans , pour in a bottle of Yakult and add more ice . Served icy cold ! Optional to add some chia seeds or other ingredients too . ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
So instead of the sweeten syrup of the canned Longans , it was replaced with Yakult . ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Healthier choice and takes less than 5 minutes to prepare . ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
